WEBVTT

00:03:26.292 --> 00:03:31.096
and in short, recreated
the malaria parasite on a chip.

00:03:31.585 --> 00:03:35.052
We did this in Africa,
and we're very proud of that.

00:03:35.379 --> 00:03:41.554
(Applause)

00:03:41.578 --> 00:03:44.689
The chip is a small glass slide,

00:03:44.713 --> 00:03:47.109
but it gives us incredible power.

00:03:48.007 --> 00:03:54.174
We simultaneously gathered data
on over 100 antibody responses.

00:03:54.592 --> 00:03:56.192
What are we looking for?

00:03:56.679 --> 00:04:01.314
The recipe behind a successful
antibody response,